            "content": "<p>We are looking to work with creators, influencers and bloggers that share our values; Passionate about storytelling, children’s literacy, and screen-free play. But more importantly who share this ethos through their content.</p><p>Voxblock is a screen-free audiobook player for children that puts stories and literacy front and centre. We believe that audio plays a vital role in helping children thrive and gearing them up for their futures. Audiobooks can be valuable resource especially for children who don’t always connect with traditional reading.</p><p>This year is the National Year of Reading, and it’s the perfect moment to highlight a message that sits at the heart of everything we do:</p><h4>All reading doesn’t look the same.</h4>"
